<v-app-bar
    v-model="bar"
    app
    hide-on-leave="false"
  >
<!--    侧边栏-->
    <v-btn
      icon
      @click="showSnackBar"
    >
      <v-icon>mdi-menu</v-icon>
    </v-btn>
<!--    返回键-->
    <v-btn
      icon
      @click="goBack"
    >
      <v-icon>mdi-arrow-left</v-icon>
    </v-btn>
<!--    标题-->
    <v-toolbar-title
      style="cursor: pointer"
      @click="goIndex"
    >
      {{ appTitle }}
    </v-toolbar-title>
    <v-spacer />
  </v-app-bar>
